{"tid":910172,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]自助餐求推介","createTime":"2018-11-21T03:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T13:26:14.000Z","uid":51387,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"453beff6c12e7ed8b0a8e8cdcfc21cbb2b842912","tid":910172,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 女朋友生日, 今年話想食自助餐, 食囉. <br />\n本來佢就指定自助山, 一個月前都book咗, 不過近日見到有巴打對自助山幾劣評, 同條女講完佢都縮縮地沙. <br />\n<br />\n問題來了, 有邊間好食? 想呢個星期六或日食嘅, 所以要快手book.<br />\n1) Cafe Too 星期六日晚都full咗<br />\n2) 暫時book咗文華東方Clipper Lounge<br />\n3) 洲際好似話唔多掂? 已ban<br />\n4) Royal Garden早兩三年食過, 發覺水準滑落<br />\n5) JW早排食過, 不考慮<br />\n<br />\nBudget: 800/位"},{"pid":"604cad17b9e3e9fc11929a5bbc28ec4ee5195e6b","tid":910172,"uid":126690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ae36d0b28218b0cadc9a285bc572b2912d70a64","tid":910172,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"Mr steak ?"},{"pid":"34f679a7b48bb1891d8bf1290834a35873359443","tid":910172,"uid":208132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"薈景"},{"pid":"14b2ec20b9e5c7a726ed85f17d5a82956b280cd8","tid":910172,"uid":97550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"都會海逸"},{"pid":"3b6626de09d8770751f5f917ca216e49d4081cc2","tid":910172,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"東薈城果間酒店 200有找"},{"pid":"eb9ce8bd76d752f3bcc2326bfae98ec264eb0c91","tid":910172,"uid":100766,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"九龍酒店<br />\n啲野幾啱我食，又唔太貴"},{"pid":"94b700bb95134f3d85b612bd323a9dbf2ab03b31","tid":910172,"uid":31051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"君悅茶園"},{"pid":"f10e52f56c8733afe6b8020a4f965b19f4fb21e6","tid":910172,"uid":25595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"Cafe103"},{"pid":"5ea3f8f1760efe3617dfe563a868349c6811db37","tid":910172,"uid":63441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"覺得逸東新開果間The Astor唔錯<br />\n超多嘢食<br />\n不過我係lunch去<br />\n感覺lunch個價位佢幾好<br />\n晚餐好似都只係多咗龍蝦之類<br />\n唔值俾多幾舊水"},{"pid":"32bba5c7f1bc472cd33736542093b753165b8de3","tid":910172,"uid":159130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"九龍酒店！夠平，嘢食唔算太多但好食，食完dinner buffet仲會送多個tea可以下次食"},{"pid":"363f7307ec94adfe65b8b680d4507d007e5a9940","tid":910172,"uid":19421,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"94b700bb95134f3d85b612bd323a9dbf2ab03b31","tid":910172,"uid":31051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"君悅茶園"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"和議"},{"pid":"98bcdb282edd6314712a0e8bade1374fcc19168c","tid":910172,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"真係文華啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 選擇可能少啲啲但質素真係非常好"},{"pid":"2bcf35d48201ab5efd6ffa1bfb393e7eaf2158bb","tid":910172,"uid":214127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"Cafe too 上次夜晚食竟然無生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0001c50ae232a87bb0841c78bd874bcbb40552ce","tid":910172,"uid":12006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"The Market？"},{"pid":"ec2c7f0efaae45c7dfdc228cb383275024c239ba","tid":910172,"uid":222814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"食過Clipper lounge Sunday brunch，冇驚喜但係質素okay嘅 自助餐應該都唔差"},{"pid":"cfaeaf5d77ebed1220c617f342a9890aeff3ab74","tid":910172,"uid":51387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"最後俾Clipper Lounge同茶園女朋友揀, 茶園跑出, 多謝各位巴打建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他冇考慮原因如下:<br />\n1) 朗豪坊(隔離間酒店?) - 怕多大陸人, 不了<br />\n2) Mr. Steak - <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3) 薈景 - 開揚過頭, 仲會見到有人上上落落, 好似大學飯堂<br />\n4) 都會海逸 - 公司年尾自助餐指定場所, 唔想兩個月內食兩次<br />\n5) 東薈城果間酒店 - 唔想同自由行迫, 價錢並非是次考慮因素<br />\n6) 九龍酒店 - 食過兩次, 水準合格, 不過合格到全部嘢太平穩冇驚喜<br />\n7) Cafe103 - 睇漏咗呢位巴打嘅推薦, 下次睇睇<br />\n8) 逸東Astor - 電話冇人聽<br />\n9) The Market - 好似要好早book定? 電話都懶得打去問"},{"pid":"e56c9777e158f46b108d5e698ca194b6414891a0","tid":910172,"uid":31051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cfaeaf5d77ebed1220c617f342a9890aeff3ab74","tid":910172,"uid":51387,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"最後俾Clipper Lounge同茶園女朋友揀, 茶園跑出, 多謝各位巴打建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其他冇考慮原因如下:<br />\n1) 朗豪坊(隔離間酒店?) - 怕多大陸人, 不了<br />\n2) Mr. Steak - <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3) 薈景 - 開揚過頭, 仲會見到有人上上落落, 好似大學飯堂<br />\n4) 都會海逸 - 公司年尾自助餐指定場所, 唔想兩個月內食兩次<br />\n5) 東薈城果間酒店 - 唔想同自由行迫, 價錢並非是次考慮因素<br />\n6) 九龍酒店 - 食過兩次, 水準合格, 不過合格到全部嘢太平穩冇驚喜<br />\n7) Cafe103 - 睇漏咗呢位巴打嘅推薦, 下次睇睇<br />\n8) 逸東Astor - 電話冇人聽<br />\n9) The Market - 好似要好早book定? 電話都懶得打去問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"茶園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得茶園雖然啲野食種類唔算話好多 但勝在樣樣高質<br />\n<br />\n個人最中意佢啲自製雪糕同各種甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鵝肝又大大舊 如果中意食生蠔既話我印象係有6款提供 雖然我自己就生唔到生蠔所以無掂過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b02544a204756f261889fad29125b7a549a849","tid":910172,"uid":31051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56c9777e158f46b108d5e698ca194b6414891a0","tid":91